              "free_text": [
                " The deltaE-E counter telescope consisting",
                "of two silicon semiconductor detectors: a totally",
                "depleted deltaE detector, 47 mu-m thick, followed by",
                "an E detector, depleted to a depth of 400 mu-m.",
                "Aluminum foils, totaling 7.6 mg/cm2 in surface",
                "density, prevented fission fragments and",
                "natural-decay alpha particles from reaching the",
                "detectors."
